net.bytebuddy.instrumentation

Class InvokeDynamic.WithImplicitArguments

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.bytebuddy.instrumentation.InvokeDynamic

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InvokeDynamic.WithImplicitTarget

    InvokeDynamic

    public static class InvokeDynamic.WithImplicitArguments
extends InvokeDynamic
    Representation of an InvokeDynamic instrumentation where the bootstrapped method is passed a this reference, if available, and any arguments of the instrumented method.

        Creates a new dynamic method invocation with implicit arguments.
        Parameters:
        bootstrapMethod - The bootstrap method.
        handleArguments - The arguments that are provided to the bootstrap method.
        invocationProvider - The target provided that identifies the method to be bootstrapped.
